subject: Tennis
United States Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: At the U.S. Open, the pressure will be on Serena Williams to achieve a milestone that has been reached only six times — by Don Budge, Maureen Connolly, Rod Laver (twice), Margaret Court and Steffi Graf.
